article.description: — Elijah Olaniyi and Tykei Greene scored 16 points apiece as Stony Brook defeated Maine 80-72 on Saturday.
article.headline: Olaniyi, Greene lead Stony Brook past Maine 80-72
article.linkText: Olaniyi, Greene lead Stony Brook past Maine 80-72
article.story: STONY BROOK, N.Y. -- — Elijah Olaniyi and Tykei Greene scored 16 points apiece as Stony Brook defeated Maine 80-72 on Saturday. Anthony Roberts added 15 points for the Seawolves. Greene also had nine rebounds. Frankie Policelli had 14 points for Stony Brook (9-5, 1-0 America East Conference), which earned its sixth consecutive home victory. Sam Ihekwoaba scored a season-high 22 points and had nine rebounds for the Black Bears (3-10, 0-2), who have now lost four consecutive games. Ja'Shonte Wright-McLeish added 15 points. Maks Klanjscek had 13 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
